    <title>Humane’s daily returns are outpacing sales</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Y5jIMu_VkfcjqfUxoOhbm_MqVVU=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73507313/247075_Humane_AI_pin_AKrales_0056.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;Photo by Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption&gt;
